      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a dependable daily driver for someone who doesn't mind a bit of character. The exterior has several noticeable dings, some fading paint on the hood, and minor rust spots around the wheel wells. Mechanically, it runs and drives fine, though it has high mileage and the interior shows significant wear on the upholstery and carpets. It\u2019s a solid, functional car that has been used regularly but is ready for its next chapter.",
